Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.54,0:51:56.76,English,,0,0,0,,watching this already, this is the first time this segment has been recorded on YouTube, YouTube.\N{\rChinese}这段录制在YouTube上是第一次。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.78,0:52:01.36,English,,0,0,0,,If this segment comes to YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube, YouTube,\N{\rChinese}如果这段录制上传到YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube，YouTube
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.22,0:52:09.36,English,,0,0,0,,YouTube, okay\N{\rChinese}YouTube，好的
